title: Tech sweeps series at Rice - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Tech sweeps series at Rice - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: HOUSTON – The No. 17 Texas Tech baseball team completed a three-game road series sweep of Rice on Sunday afternoon, defeating the Owls 7-4 at Reckling Park. The Red Raiders return home winning four of five games during their seven-day road trip.
